TRAIT.name = "Ecologist 2: Artifact Hunter"
TRAIT.description = "In the search for the Zone's artifacts, the Ecologists enjoy both expertise and experience.\nUpon achieving this Trait, you may request a lead on a rare artifact from the Ecologists, leading to an event chain. Upon use, this trait resets Ecologist Reputation to 15, allowing you to regain rep and gain another use of this trait. This can be repeated."
